name: PufDAO
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
The genesis DAO on Arbitrum.

What makes your project unique?
We have an extremely active and loyal community. Sold out two NFT collections on Arbitrum and 1 on zkSync.

History of your project.
Stealth launching in mid-February, PufDAO marketed hard to gain a large portion of Arbitrum’s NFT market share.

What’s next for your project?
We do what makes sense. No roadmap. No official communities made by us besides Twitter. We have active members creating discords, telegrams, websites, etc. 

What can your token be used for?
No utility. Meme token.
